setUp().details: Uses modified version of NonfungiblePositionManager to allow for modifications of the pool. Original code enforces a check that a pool's bytecode was not modified for security purposes.Imports are reliant on specific versioning to avoid compiler errors: v3-core : release 0.8 v3-periphery : release 0.8 openzeppelin-contracts : release release-v4.0

setUp().notice: Sets up a Uniswapv3 pool with: two tokens of 18 decimal places, starting price of 1 tokenA/tokenB, and liquidty across the whole tick range.
